d to continue with the rest of the pre-flight audit steps (we have done 1.1-1.6, 1.8-1.12 partially). We need to finish step 1 (all substeps) before moving to step 2.\n\nLet's proceed.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-b23e4e43f2d2f962","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 1.7 Postgres roles and databases (read-only query) ===\" && docker exec postgres psql -U hermes -d forgejo -c \"\\du\" -c \"\\l\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b","usage":{"input":67047,"output":545,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67592,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778108014526,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b8ce12ffb4f6b2e3"}}
